summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from N. H. Latimer and Margaret Latimer, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle dated the 14th day of November, 1902, to Lots Thirteen (13), Fourteen (14), Fifteen (15), Twenty-one (21) and Twenty-two (22) in Block "F" of Phinney's Addition to the City of Seattle.
